{"tid":1610672,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無得反利用狼來了既戰術？","createTime":"2019-10-01T18:58:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T15:21:38.000Z","uid":73722,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6bf183d9ff97853c36161de3d2a2596496f46962","tid":1610672,"uid":73722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T18:58:11.000Z","msg":"最近見到開始多post提醒full gear既手足要勇敢d（雖然係言語偽術都希望大家開post可以用下，唔好因為想搶focus或者嬲就做標題黨），但每次玩online game有人叫有狗都會退<br />\n<br />\n倒不如在場既真勇武有預感下波怪物來襲前就大叫「有速龍/有狗」睇下到底在場幾多隊友係敢打怪，幾多想退後支援，最少心入面有個底先，此舉有兩個好處<br />\n<br />\n1.如果係敢打怪既，無論你嗌咩佢地都唔會退<br />\n<br />\n係想係後面支援既，又唔洗令真勇武手足對人手失算，大家都知啦，怪物難打要夠人先打得架<br />\n<br />\n2.你叫得多，大家都對速龍上黎有個心理準備<br />\n有追下其他post都知有唔少手足心熊準備不足，一句說話比加油更能提神，何樂而不為<br />\n<br />\n但一個最大既壞處就係：有無怪大家係有眼睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4882c1062ae897f7865ac5d94934cc0eceb6d37","tid":1610672,"uid":215700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:01:28.000Z","msg":"手足 唔係想分化<br />\n不過用下腦先開post啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e885f3284e8cbcc1ff101f06635a8ae636beda1e","tid":1610672,"uid":119478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:05:37.000Z","msg":"害撚死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef4b6afc44529f6fc7e541ce4b09878590377f76","tid":1610672,"uid":206370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:26:50.000Z","msg":"比錯正評 屌你啊？無腦？"},{"pid":"496c51b688e786da69cefba3bfb9bea1980bb694","tid":1610672,"uid":25290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:28:16.000Z","msg":"痴撚線，狼來了"},{"pid":"b8dbfebf79e848ac81fe4e5eb8e99ac87b40547e","tid":1610672,"uid":19252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:32:47.000Z","msg":"以為你咁勁對狗用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不推文"},{"pid":"cb63f8ce0887016322094f891fe1460596ad3e44","tid":1610672,"uid":135390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:33:34.000Z","msg":"不如咁講,下次跟隊打波唔好等班狗衝,個個向後跑先叫<br />\n係佢地未衝前個陣就組定隊,話比自己友知到底有幾多人係敢上前<br />\n如果多既就一齊上,少既就準備好後路,同時試下叫多d前線升級做勇武"},{"pid":"453db1bf5655fe279439521c71fb7f6ebc8dec07","tid":1610672,"uid":73722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T20:22:30.000Z","msg":"我都負評自己不推文自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日發夢望住班full gear但一句有狗就衝去後排支援既手足<br />\n我承認自己失左智<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5794ac07bc2c8ce5c54931abb3dfdad89291ce5b","tid":1610672,"uid":73722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T20:24:14.000Z","msg":"仲有黃大仙個post真係越睇越嬲"},{"pid":"021c29abface17a74f8a2884f23d9f044aba502d","tid":1610672,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:21:38.000Z","msg":"銀髮軍師 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">和理非</span>加入 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">戰況大增</span>千倍的新戰術<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1613583\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1613583</a>"}]}